ament.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aActresseszGreat BritainxHistory. 0aActresseszGreat Britain. 0aMotion picture actors and actresseszGreat Britain. 0aMotion pictures for womenzGreat Britain. 0aWomen in motion pictures. 4aFilm, Media & Cultural Studies. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Acting & Auditioning.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEdinburgh University Press Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311078140340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781474405652?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781474405652423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781474405652/original  a978-3-11-078140-3  Edinburgh University Press Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MUAR  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK